    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and all major systems are in full working order, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. While the exterior is generally clean, you may find a few small stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved with no tears in the upholstery, though there is some minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and steering wheel. Overall, it\u2019s a solid, honest car that offers a great balance of performance and value.",
