    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and usage. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that feels a bit soft over bumps. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation who doesn't mind putting in a little work to refresh its appearance.",
