    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly flawless condition\u2014inside and out! It drives like a dream and looks just as sharp as the day it was first bought. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been totally pampered and is ready for a new home, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
